sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Employer as Employer (multisig)
    participant Orc as TS Orchestrator
    participant PT as Payday PTB
    participant Pay as Payroll (shared)
    participant Esc as TaxEscrow (shared)
    participant Sca as MockScallopVault
    participant Nav as MockNaviVault
    participant Pyth as Pyth (real)
    actor Emp as Employee

    Employer->>Orc: click "Run Payroll"
    Orc->>Pyth: read FX price (publish_time)
    Note over Orc,Pyth: D9: stale (>60s) → fx_stale flag, NOT abort<br/>FX is reporting-only, not in value path
    Orc->>PT: build N branches (≤50/PTB), key list + PythPrice
    PT->>Pay: begin_period(cap) — current_period += 1 (once per payday, D10)
    loop per employee (pay_one)
        PT->>Pay: split gross from funding (abort if short)
        PT->>Esc: reserve(jurisdiction, withholding)
        Note over PT,Pay: net = gross - withholding<br/>read committed AllocationConfig for current_period<br/>lazy-promote this record's pending if due (D10)
        alt scallop.active
            PT->>Sca: mint(scallop_amt) -> sCoin
            Sca-->>Emp: transfer Coin<MockSCoin<USDC>>
        else inactive (D8)
            Note over PT: scallop_amt folds into liquid
        end
        alt navi.active
            PT->>Nav: deposit(beneficiary=Emp, navi_amt)
            Note over Nav: positions[Emp] += amt (address-keyed)
        else inactive (D8)
            Note over PT: navi_amt folds into liquid
        end
        PT-->>Emp: transfer liquid Coin<USDC>
        PT->>PT: emit PayrollEventV1 (sum-check: gross == wh+liq+sca+navi; +fx_stale)
    end
    PT-->>Employer: one tx hash / explorer URL
    Emp->>Pay: set_ratios via AllocationCap (staged → effective next period, D10)
